## What is it?
A Python script that runs in the background and automatically delivers the best Bug Bounty writeups straight to your Discord server every hour without spamming.

## Features & Advantages
* **Zero Dependencies:** Built entirely using Python's standard library (`stdlib`). No `pip install` required!
* **Anti-Spam Mechanism:** Uses a local database (`sent.log`) to track sent IDs and ensure zero duplicates.
* **Smart Queue:** Keeps writeups sorted by quality/trust level so you only read the best stuff.

## Installation
```bash
git clone [https://github.com/0xdragon/bitthewriteup](https://github.com/0xdragon/bitthewriteup)
cd bitthewriteup
cp config.example.json config.json
